MessageDestination

public MessageDestination(String destinationID)
TODO: Eventually this constructor must be removed alongside with "removeComponent()" method and DestinationType must be exclusively used. Currently this constructor can not be removed because there are places where MessageDestination is constructed from a tokenizer created from Message.toString(). In order to remove this constructor, message construction from string should be avoided. - Maniy
